metadata.dc:description: A case of a patients is presented that consults for sharp abdominal pain that is intervened surgically with extirpation of a mass that commits the right annex. Histological preparations showed confirms ovarian pregnancy.
metadata.dc:title: Embarazo ectopico en ovario (informe de un caso).
[Primary ovarian pregnancy (case report)].
metadata.dc:publisher: Revista de la Facultad de Ciencias Medicas (Cordoba, Argentina)
